Dataset (Simple Mediation Model)

Source: R/data.R
simple_med.Rd

Generated from a simple mediation model, n = 200

Usage

simple_med

Format

A data frame with 200 rows and three variables:

x

x, the independent variable

m

m, the mediator

y

y, the dependent variable

Details

This model is used for examples like this one:

library(lavaan)
mod <- "m ~ x
        y ~ m"
fit <- cfa(mod, simple_med)
summary(fit)

Examples


print(head(simple_med), digits = 3)
#>        x      m     y
#> 1 -0.345   7.28 -5.64
#> 2 -0.366  -5.45 -4.53
#> 3 -0.829  -7.02 -7.82
#> 4 -0.339   4.37  1.56
#> 5 -0.963  -4.02 -7.29
#> 6 -1.075 -11.54 -4.15
nrow(simple_med)
#> [1] 200
